01:05:51.890 --> 01:05:57.600
2m l squared v0
over h bar squared.

01:05:57.600 --> 01:06:01.237
So this is h bar squared, 1 over
l squared is k squared over 2m,

01:06:01.237 --> 01:06:02.070
