01:07:03.230 --> 01:07:10.960
squared of g0 square
root of epsilon minus 1.

01:07:15.400 --> 01:07:16.645
And upstairs is a one.

01:07:21.900 --> 01:07:24.270
So remember this is only
valid for e greater than v0,

01:07:24.270 --> 01:07:26.630
or equivalently,
