and for some fixed g0.

01:07:59.460 --> 01:08:01.960
Keep in mind that this only
makes sense for e greater

01:08:01.960 --> 01:08:04.564
than v0 or for epsilon
greater than 1, so here's 1.

01:08:04.564 --> 01:08:05.980
And we're going
to remain agnostic

01:08:05.980 --> 01:08:08.780
as to what happens below 1.

