OK.

01:10:05.824 --> 01:10:07.240
And now what
happens, for example,

01:10:07.240 --> 01:10:09.780
for a very large epsilon?

01:10:09.780 --> 01:10:14.430
Well, when epsilon is gigantic,
sine squared of this-- well,

01:10:14.430 --> 01:10:15.930
sine squared is
