01:12:15.610 --> 01:12:18.040
As epsilon goes
larger and larger,

01:12:18.040 --> 01:12:21.440
this deviation become
smaller and smaller.

01:12:21.440 --> 01:12:23.250
So that's what this
plot is telling us.

01:12:23.250 --> 01:12:25.400
This plot is telling
us a bunch of things.

01:12:25.400 --> 01:12:31.440
First off, we see that
at large energies,

01:12:31.440 --> 01:12:32.462
